    "org_about":  "Üsküdar University is considered one of the distinguished private universities in Turkey in the fields of health sciences, medicine, psychology, and engineering. Located in Istanbul, the university was established in 2011 and is known for its strong focus on scientific research, neuroscience, and behavioral sciences. It also includes modern research centers and laboratories used for students’ practical training.",
