                                    "header":  "Eligibility criteria",
                                    "body":  "\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"f0ea146e-af52-46b4-ad20-91bf57481372\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-5-5\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"100\" data-start=\"0\"\u003eInternational students can apply to the university programs if they meet the following requirements:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"724\" data-start=\"102\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"171\" data-section-id=\"idy8kw\" data-start=\"102\"\u003eHolding a high school diploma for Bachelor\u0026rsquo;s degree applications.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"237\" data-section-id=\"7xfaqi\" data-start=\"172\"\u003eHolding a Bachelor\u0026rsquo;s degree for Master\u0026rsquo;s degree applications.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"289\" data-section-id=\"1c3jic\" data-start=\"238\"\u003eHolding a Master\u0026rsquo;s degree for PhD applications.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"318\" data-section-id=\"t9kep2\" data-start=\"290\"\u003eHaving a valid passport.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"355\" data-section-id=\"kfipxy\" data-start=\"319\"\u003eSubmitting academic transcripts.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"427\" data-section-id=\"1kobnlz\" data-start=\"356\"\u003eProviding an English or Turkish language certificate, if available.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"594\" data-section-id=\"1kyu5f3\" data-start=\"428\"\u003eStudents may apply without IELTS for some programs, with the possibility of taking a university language proficiency exam or studying a preparatory language year.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"724\" data-section-id=\"zcn40w\" data-start=\"595\"\u003eSome medical majors or graduate programs may require a high academic GPA or additional requirements depending on the program.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"893\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"726\"\u003eIn addition, \u0026Uuml;sk\u0026uuml;dar University welcomes students from various nationalities, especially Arab and international students wishing to study in Turkey.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-is-intersecting=\"true\" data-turn-id-container=\"request-WEB:b8708eed-80f2-4187-8a29-f1a94a8d3768-24\"\u003e\u003csection data-scroll-anchor=\"false\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-50\" data-turn=\"assistant\" data-turn-id=\"request-WEB:b8708eed-80f2-4187-8a29-f1a94a8d3768-24\" data-turn-id-container=\"request-WEB:b8708eed-80f2-4187-8a29-f1a94a8d3768-24\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"e65dbffd-92f3-44cf-9a6f-4bb142ff36eb\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-5-5\" data-turn-start-message=\"true\" dir=\"auto\" tabindex=\"0\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"81\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"0\"\u003eDiscover the top \u003ca href=\"https://www.for9a.com/learn/%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AD-%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B3%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D9%85%D9%85%D9%88%D9%84%D8%A9-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%83%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%84-2026-%D8%A8%D8%AF%D9%88%D9%86-%D8%A7%D9%8A%D9%84%D8%AA%D8%B3\"\u003e20 fully funded scholarships\u003c/a\u003e for 2026 that do not require IELTS\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e"
